::Prowl::

Prowl looked into IR's eyes with love and kissed her again. "I love you," he says to her, giving her a small squeze and then looking at Maximal City. The thoughts of her being stronger than him as a Prime were dormant for now.

He looks back at her, smiles, and begins to walk toward the city, her still in his arms.

> city.
